    "description": "<p>You can spend 1 minute observing or interacting with a creature out of Combat (or spend <strong>1 AP</strong> in Combat) to learn information about its physical capabilities compared to your own.</p><p>Choose one of the following stats of the creature to assess:</p><ul><li><p>Might</p></li><li><p>Agility</p></li><li><p>PD</p></li><li><p>PDR</p></li><li><p>HP</p></li></ul><p>Make a <strong>DC 10 Knowledge</strong> or <strong>Insight Check</strong> (your choice).</p><p><strong>Success:</strong> You learn if the chosen stat is higher, lower, or the same as yours.</p>",
